{
  "name": "Stars After Death [S-Rank]",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/squares-3d-green.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The first time this creature would fall to 0 Hit points, they reactively draw the symbol of the Star village on the ground. <br />Their body dies, but their spirit solidifies onto the material plane. <br />This spirit using all of their same statistics of their living body, but cannot be harmed by any damage type except Chakra, Force or Psychic. <br />Their Spirit has a number of hit points equal to half of maximum and unlimited Chakra. <br />Regardless of its remaining or current hit points, it dies and passes on to the other world after a number of rounds equal to [Charisma modifier + 1d4].</p>",
